name: 東江
message: "You won't kill me. Not now. If you do, you'll have to continue living in a world without kin or purpose."

name: 東江
message: "As dark a hell as I can imagine. In which case... why not join me? It hardly makes a difference now."

name: 東江
message: "I've won. That means fate is on my side. And so, I will keep following my path. I can do no less."

name: 東江
message: "You are the last of your people. You escaped me once, but your rightful place was always in my power."

name: 東江
message: "Things will simply be as they should have been. Perfectly natural. Perfectly."

name: 東江
message: "I know it troubles you. But this is fate."

name: ミンク
message: "Oh, it worked. Your 'seed' is firmly planted in my mind."

name: ミンク
message: "For a second there, it all went black. Despair almost crushed me."

name: ミンク
message: "But it turns out someone else planted a seed before you."

name: ミンク
message: "Doubt he even knows what he did."

name: ミンク
message: "But his seed was stronger than yours. Can't beat the real thing, yeah?"
